  "stemHtml": "Refer to figures. <br /> You are planning an ambulance flight where a patient needs to be transported from one hospital to another. The flight has been declared by a medical authority as being a medical flight where special handling due to the status of the flight is requested. What are you going to enter in field 18 of your ATS flight plan?",
